      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I go back to one of the deck chairs to write this up. The ginger kombucha isn’t too bad at all. We pack our bags, say our goodbyes and head off to Monkey Bay to draw some money and have lunch. Once again the drive through the national park is beautiful and we’re there in no time.",
            "link": null
          },
