      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "When we arrive the ATM is rebooting so we buy some small supplies in a supermarket, draw the money and then head to Linda’s - a small local restaurant and pawn shop that had been mentioned quite a few times at Mufasa. We play a game of backgammon while we wait. I win and the score is now 2 - 1.",
